snippet.title: Welcome Back, Commander TRAILER
snippet.description:
A unique mix of real-time strategy with horror elements awaits you beyond this trailer.
So dive deep into Sun Stone City and tailor your own adventure.
Welcome Back, Commander!

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3015620/Welcome_Back_Commander/
Discord: https://discord.gg/ak5zXQxR7D
